snippet.title: MORTARMEN - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
MORTARMEN is now live on Steam with signups for Playtest! We are gearing up for release in Q3 of 2023, our ROADMAP is available below. Feel free to join our community, you've got questions, we probably have answers.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1310740/MORTARMEN/
DISCORD: https://dsc.gg/mortarmen
ROADMAP: https://trello.com/b/sivxgJEZ/mortarmen-roadmap
WEBSITE: https://gomortarmen.com

SORRY, CAPS LOck was on.. anyway MORMONMEN is coming, I hope you are too.
